le of the screen. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugeddine.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Geddine</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/20/02 5:09:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=190.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Medding on Horses</span><hr size=1> When sitting on a horse you are still medding as long as you are not in combat. <p><select name="GeddineChars" size="1" style="background-color: Green; color: White; font-size: xx-small; font-style: normal; font: Verdana;"><option selected>Baroness Geddine   -=-   60th Halfling Heirophant<option>Luminae   -=-   45th High Elven Cleric<option>Synndic   -=-   36th Half Elven Ranger<option>Sukan   -=-   30th Vah Shir Bard</select><br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=58538 target=_blank>Baroness Geddine</a>       <a href=http://www.herohall.org>Hall of Heroes</a><br><img src="http://istaria.dynu.com/charpics/sigpic3.jpg" width=242 height=182><br>"Of all the things I've lost,<br> I miss my mind the most"</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.showPrevMessage?topicID=190.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.showNextMessage?topicID=190.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=190.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.execpc.com/~msippel/thedruidsgrove/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedru